.action
  |  You use #{data.items[msg.item].name} on 
  if msg.sender_slug === msg.target_slug
    | yourself
  else
    | <a href='/profile/#{msg.target_slug}'>#{msg.target_name}</a>
  | , healing #{msg.amount} HP.
  if _.contains(character.skills, 'triage')
    if msg.remaining > 0
      |  #{msg.remaining} HP remains unhealed. 
    else
      |  No HP remains unhealed. 
  div.time= moment(msg.sent).fromNow()
